  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Alacarte</title>

    <para>
      <application>Alacarte</application> is a menu editor for
      <application>GNOME</application> Desktop using the
      freedesktop.org menu specification.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

